Class Project1

java.lang.Object
Project1
public class Project1
extends java.lang.Object
This program creates a window and adds data to that window from a text file We read a text file filled with clock times and we display that in a two column grid layout The first column is for the unsorted times of the text file The second column is for the sorted times of the text file
Author:
Bola Gadalla
